\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 16\tab Accordingly, MCNSW was entitled to requisition a meeting under clause 41.  There is no other objection t
o the validity of its requisition.  In my judgment, its requisition was a valid one. 
