\par }\pard \qj \li1440\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin1440\itap0 {\f0\fs20\cf1\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 I think a Council meeting at the very least will allow you to consider the wishes of Council members on key matters.  
